---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About China Unlocked"
	description="China Signals explained for global readers."
	pubDate={new Date('June 07 2026')}
>
	<p>
		China Unlocked is an English-language briefing project that turns domestic Chinese social
		signals into clear context for readers outside the Chinese internet.
	</p>

	<p>
		The daily China Signals workflow monitors trend sources such as Douyin, Weibo, and
		Xiaohongshu, then reframes the strongest items as explainers: what happened, why it moved,
		what outsiders often miss, and what to watch next.
	</p>

	<p>
		This site is designed for curious readers, founders, creators, analysts, and anyone who wants
		to understand China beyond recycled headlines. Every item should be treated as a starting
		signal, not a final verdict: sensitive or rumor-prone topics need human review before wider
		distribution.
	</p>
</Layout>
